body.name: Timberland Men's Classic Leather Reversible Belt
features: Origin Made in the USA and Imported

MEN’S 100% REVERSIBLE LEATHER BELT: Timberland reversible belt for men is made with 100% genuine leather and has a single-loop silver buckle design and feathered edges. It’s a perfect everyday casual mens belt leather. The belt width is 1.4 inch

CASUAL OR DRESS BELT: This leather mens belt is a versatile belt, it’s the perfect mens belt for jeans but easily converts into a dress belt. The precision manufacturing ensures durability, making it a great work belt as well as a mens belt casual

ONE BELT TWO COLORS: The Timberland Men’s Reversible Leather Belt is reversible and has one black side and one brown side. You can purchase one belt and get a black mens belt and a brown mens belt for the price of one

THE PERFECT FIT (BIG AND TALL SIZES AVAILABLE): For a perfect fit be sure to order 1 size larger than your pant size. If your pant size is a 36 order a belt size 38. Also men’s belts big and tall sizes are available, sizes 44 to 56.

HIGH-QUALITY CONSTRUCTION: Timberland products are made to last. High-quality genuine leather, tight stitching, and precision manufacturing allow this mens leather belt to hold up to extensive and frequent use.
body.description: For those working on the job site, going to the office or simply walking around town, do so in style while you wear a Timberland belt for men. This Timberland Men’s Reversible Leather Brown Black Belt is made from 100% genuine leather and has a silver single-loop buckle. This men’s leather belt can transition from a men’s jean belt but can also be converted to be worn as a mens dress belt with slacks. Manufactured with classically cut edges and a single-prong buckle, this daily men’s leather belt simply looks great, and it’s designed to last a long time. The Timberland Men’s Classic Leather Jean Belt features feathered edges and pairs well with high-quality jeans and Timberland boots Timberland products are designed to last for extended periods of frequent use. Our mens belts are made from high-quality genuine leather and stitched with precision manufacturing standards, which helps them hold up to frequent and extensive use. The durable construction and superior materials also withstand cold and hot weather alike, making this a perfect all-season work belt or casual belt. This street-worthy mens leather belt by Timberland is made to fit to your daily schedule and lifestyle comfortably. It is smooth to the touch and has a sharp and rich color. Timberland offers this men’s belts in different sizes. Looking for a mens brown belt or mens black belt we have you covered. Don’t sacrifice when looking for a leather belt for men. Our Timberland Mens belts for jeans are inspired by a rich and traditional New England heritage, and the quality they produce in each product is legendary. This genuine leather jean belt is offered in big and tall sizes and multiple colors. For a precision fit, it’s best to order it one size larger than your pants. Don’t settle with a no name mens casual belt, get the best mens belt available from a trusted brand like Timberland. Our quality and craftsmanship makes our jean belt for men the perfect belt for all men.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewText: Most belts I buy say all leather but I find out all too soon that it’s bonded. They wear out quickly and look shabby. This belt says all leather and it looks like it is now The jury is still out. I’ll let you know but I think it is 100% Leather.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 12, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Looks good and really good material

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on April 2, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Looks good doesn't last
reviews.reviewText: I have purchased 2 of these belts for my son.The price was right ✅️While they look really good they all broke within 6 months 😔 👎I repurchased after the 1st one broke thinking sometimes these things happen but after the 2nd one broke...Nope

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 3, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars high quality dress belt in black and brown with reversible buckle
reviews.reviewText: Timberland quality at a super price. High quality leather which is highly durable but yet extremely pliable and comfortable. High quality buckle with extremely easy reversibility for having a black or brown belt compatible to whatever color you need to match your outfit.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 11, 2024
reviews.reviewText: The buckle turn colors after a few months

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 28, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars two belts in one
reviews.reviewText: I like the fact that the belt is reversible and so does the son who this was purchased for. Definitely get your monies worth. It's hard to beat the price for a leather belt nowadays; usually you'll pay this price or more for the "pleather/vegan" belt. Arrived on time and in padded/bubble mailer.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 6, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Real Leather Belt
reviews.reviewText: Real leather belt with durable reversible buckle. Worn a dozen times and like it.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Broke after 2 months
reviews.reviewText: Wore it nearly daily for 2 months and the clasp broke when fastening it one night after going to the restroom while out in public.

reviews.reviewTitle: Top quality belt for a great price
reviews.reviewText: Iwas looking for a belt that could double as a casual with jeans or step up to business casual with my khakis. This is a truly good quality belt of solid leather. I like that it is reversible by simply flipping the buckle to switch it from black to brown. I trusted the sizing chart on the recommendation to order one size larger. It fits great.
O cinto é um pouco mais fino do que eu esperava mas não deixa de ser um cinto bonito, material muito bom e versátil por ser dupla face.
Beautiful belt! Reverses from brown to black with the twist of the belt buckle. Leather and very well made. Would definitely recommend.
